TITLE: Configure Playground with Config Object vs Params
DESCRIPTION: Compares two different approaches to configure a LiveCodes playground: using a config object or using URL query parameters.
SOURCE: https://github.com/live-codes/livecodes/blob/develop/docs/docs/sdk/js-ts.mdx#2025-04-13_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { createPlayground } from 'livecodes';

// use config
createPlayground('#container', {
  config: {
    markup: {
      language: 'markdown',
      content: '# Hello World!',
    },
  },
});

// use params
createPlayground('#container', { params: { md: '# Hello World!' } });
```

