TITLE: Creating a LiveCodes Playground with Custom Module and Type Definitions
DESCRIPTION: JavaScript code showing how to create a LiveCodes playground that provides both implementation and type definitions for a custom module. It configures the playground with custom imports and types for intellisense support.
SOURCE: https://github.com/live-codes/livecodes/blob/develop/docs/docs/features/intellisense.mdx#2025-04-13_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: js
